<br/><h1 class="helpHead1"><a name="d15352e7"><!-- --></a><span id="topic-title"><a name="topic-title"><!-- --></a>What is a ProductComponent?</span></h1> 
<div> 
<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" summary="Salesforce editions needed for the documented functionality" width="100%" class="editionTable"> 
<tbody> 
</tbody> 
</table> 
<p> 
ProductComponent are individual items that you create to relate a Product and Component. This acts as link to relate many Products with many Components. This holds the details of all the Components that form the Product. </p> 
<p> 
The ProductComponent related list of a Product lists the Components for that Product. Use this related list to create new ProductComponent for a Product or edit an existing one.</p> 
</div> 
