<p id="ToAccount"><a name="ToAccount"><!-- --></a> 
<p> To create a New ProductComponent </p> 
<li>    Select a Product, in the Product detail page click on <b>New ProductComponent</b>.</li> 
<li>    Select a Component from the pop-up list.</li> 
<li>    Enter a value for Quantity (the value should be within the range of Maximum Assembly Quantity and Minimum Assembly Quantity of the component). Enter other information.</li> 
<li>    Click save when you are finished.</li> 
</p></div> 
