<p id="ToAccount"><a name="ToAccount"><!-- --></a> 
<p><b> Displaying Product components</b></p> 
<p> 
<font color="red">Product components are displayed as related list in the product detail page. </font>Click the Code to display detailed information about the ProductComponent. </p> 
<p><b>Editing Product components</b></p> 
<p> 
There are two ways to update ProductComponents, you can either edit one ProductComponent at a time or you can also perform a multi line edit for all the ProductComponents of a Product.</p> 
<p> 
To edit one ProductComponent, click on the Edit link next to the ProductComponent in the related list or you can click the Edit button on the ProductComponent detail page. Click on save when you are finished.</p> 
<p> 
To edit ProductComponents of a Product, click on the Edit button in the related list next to the New ProductComponent button. Click on save when you are finished.</p> 
<p><b>Product component Related Lists</b></p> 
<p> 
There are no specific related lists for a ProductComponent. The default related lists can be found below the ProductComponent detail.</p> 
</p></div> 
